She dodges most of the fire from the ground.  One shot hit her in the 
talon.  She kept going but the fire was coming from above her. She 
saw Sixshot flying down.  She Shreeked as her talon was in pain. She  
fly around the trees near where Ares was standing.  She swooped down 
and dived again at Ares with her good talon outstretched.
